*! Name      : lfRecPLock
*! Developer : Samah Wilson Kirollos
*! Date      : 07/18/96
*! 컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴        
*! Purpose   : Do the phisical lock on the used record 
*! 컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴
*! Passed :
*!        Parameters : 
*!           lcFile : The used file where we lock a record
*! 컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴
*! Called from : 
*!         Function : lfPhyLock
*!*************************************************************
FUNCTION lfRecPLock
PARAMETERS lcFile

DO CASE
  CASE lcFile = 'Fabric'
    lcStr = 'Item record '
  CASE lcFile = 'FabDye'
    lcStr = 'Item dyelot record '
  CASE lcFile = 'MatInvJl'
    lcStr = 'Item receiving lot record '
ENDCASE

SET REPROCESS TO 5 SECONDS 
DO WHILE .T.
  lnChoice =gfModalGen('QRM36057B36005','ALERT',lcStr) 
  IF lnChoice = 1 
    IF !RLOCK(lcFile)
      LOOP
    ELSE
      lnRet = .T.
      EXIT
    ENDIF 
  ELSE
    lnRet = .F.
    EXIT   
  ENDIF
ENDDO
  
SET REPROCESS TO 0
RETURN (lnRet)

